{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1430533, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我们最后所有人都没下井，在井口参观了一下。", "timestamp": 1618112281, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430544, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多少沾点", "timestamp": 1618112369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430548, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对面领导是以安全为由拒绝的，但和工人访谈的时候那个伯伯说了实话。", "timestamp": 1618112387, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430561, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就接待我们的人都挺好，其他场景也不会说不尊重女性什么的，但在这种迷信的文化也没有办法，唉。", "timestamp": 1618112455, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430574, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "打拳啊，凭什么女性就不能下井！", "timestamp": 1618112585, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "心里暗暗祈祷这些工人生命长久", "timestamp": 1618112922, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没什么办法吧，cz家长之前是搞铁路隧道的，去过很多施工现场，毕竟都是工人，很多这些所谓迷信之类的，影响也不算坏，也只能维持现状罢了，毕竟全国那么多工地", "timestamp": 1618113029, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430626, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这事情在矿山、隧道领域挺普遍的，工人不准女的进隧道，不吉利，女领导视察也不准进，没办法，这年头是工人不好招，干不顺心换个工地接着干，不同意不行。", "timestamp": 1618113118, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1430814, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "真的生气", "timestamp": 1618114939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想起了修红旗渠的铁姑娘队", "timestamp": 1618117207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431526, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 280531, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为提高生育率，应降低男女比例，禁止女性从事危险工作", "timestamp": 1618120073, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 280531, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "#202775\n矿山工作这事其实挺离谱的，我们之前去一个矿山社会实践，男生能下井参观女生不行。什么原因呢？女生如果生理期下井阴气重不吉利。", "timestamp": 1618112238, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618120073, "url": "", "vote": {}}}